### Get all menu items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem
Content-Type: application/json


### Create a new menu item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spaghetti Carbonara",
  "description": "Classic Italian pasta with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and pepper.",
  "price": 10.50,
  "reviews": []
}

###

### Get newly created menu item by ID (replace NEW_ID after creation)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem/NEW ITEM ID
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update a menu item by ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem/671f5b92f21a1a1b1d9a1002
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Grilled Chicken Sandwich Deluxe",
  "description": "Juicy grilled chicken with lettuce, tomato, and special sauce.",
  "price": 7.49,
  "reviews": []
}

###

### Delete a menu item by ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem/671f5b92f21a1a1b1d9a1005
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Add a review to a menu item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem/671f5b92f21a1a1b1d9a1001/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerName": "Alice Johnson",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Absolutely fantastic pizza!",
  "createdAt": "2025-10-10T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Get reviews for a menu item
GET http://localhost:5000/api/MenuItem/671f5b92f21a1a1b1d9a1001/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
